org.miniauth.oauth.common

Class OAuthOutgoingRequestBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.miniauth.oauth.common.OAuthOutgoingRequestBuilder

  • public final class OAuthOutgoingRequestBuilder
extends Object
    Builds an OAuthOutgoingRequest object. (a) Construct OAuthOutgoingRequestBuilder or call init() on existing Builder. (b) Set attributes. Note that later setter call overwrites any previously set values. (c) Then, call build() to create OAuthOutgoingRequest.
